[{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"CurrentModule = KhepriRevit","category":"page"},{"location":"#KhepriRevit","page":"Home","title":"KhepriRevit","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"A Khepri backend for Autodesk Revit, communicating via a C# plugin over TCP (port 11001).","category":"page"},{"location":"#Architecture","page":"Home","title":"Architecture","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"KhepriRevit is a SocketBackend using the :CS (C#) binary protocol. It targets Revit's BIM-native workflow with levels, system families, and loadable families.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Backend type: SocketBackend{RVTKey, Int64}\nReference IDs: Int64 (Revit ElementId values)\nCoordinate system: Right-handed Z-up (no transforms needed)\nUnit conversion: Internal to_feet constant (≈3.28084) for Revit's imperial unit system","category":"page"},{"location":"#Key-Features","page":"Home","title":"Key Features","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"BIM-native families: Three family types — RevitSystemFamily (walls, slabs), RevitFileFamily (loadable .rfa), and RevitInPlaceFamily\nLevel management: Elevation-based level creation and assignment\nBoolean operations: Full CSG support (HasBooleanOps{true})\nIFC interoperability: Import/export via convert_ifc_file() and load_rvt_file()\nBIM elements: Walls, floors, roofs, doors, windows, columns, beams, railings, fixtures","category":"page"},{"location":"#Setup","page":"Home","title":"Setup","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"using KhepriRevit\nusing KhepriBase\n\nbackend(revit)\n\n# Standard Khepri operations work transparently\nwall(xy(0, 0), xy(10, 0))\nslab(rectangular_path(xy(0, 0), 10, 8))","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Requires Revit with the Khepri C# plugin installed and listening on TCP port 11001.","category":"page"},{"location":"#Dependencies","page":"Home","title":"Dependencies","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"KhepriBase: Core Khepri functionality\nSockets: TCP communication","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Modules = [KhepriRevit]","category":"page"}]
